⚡️Plump lip hack ⚡️

On moisturized makeup free lips, take a nude lip pencil and over-line the top portion of your cupids bow and bottom lip. Don’t fill in your lips with lipliner or lipstick. Finish it off with a clear gloss. You’re welcome 🫶

Products used: 
@maccosmetics lip pencil in Whirl
@laneige_us lip glowy balm in Berry
